params.sqlcmd: "SELECT " +" PUCH_ODR_CD, " +" PLANT_CD, " +" PLANT_NAME, " +" WH_CD, " +" WH_NAME, " +" ITEM_CD, " +" ITEM_NAME, " +" COMPANY_CD, " +" VEND_CD, " +" VEND_ANAME, " +" VEND_NAME, " +" PUCH_ODR_PERSON, " +" USER_NAME, " +" FNCGETFORMATTEDDATETIME(PUCH_ODR_START_DATE) AS \\"PUCH_ODR_START_DATE\\", " +" FNCGETFORMATTEDDATETIME(PUCH_ODR_DLV_DATE) AS \\"PUCH_ODR_DLV_DATE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(PUCH_ODR_QTY, 'fm99999999999990.0999') AS \\"PUCH_ODR_QTY\\", " +" STOCK_UNIT, " +" UNIT_COST_TYP, " +" TO_CHAR(UNIT_COST, 'fm99999999999990.0099') AS \\"UNIT_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(PUCH_ODR_AMOUNT, 'fm99999999999990.0099') AS \\"PUCH_ODR_AMOUNT\\", " +" VEND_CUR_UNIT, " +" TO_CHAR(DISC_AMOUNT, 'fm99999999999990.0099') AS \\"DISC_AMOUNT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(NET_AMOUNT, 'fm99999999999990.0099') AS \\"NET_AMOUNT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(TAX_AMOUNT_1, 'fm99999999999990.0099') AS \\"TAX_AMOUNT_1\\", " +" TO_CHAR(TAX_AMOUNT_2, 'fm99999999999990.0099') AS \\"TAX_AMOUNT_2\\", " +" TO_CHAR(TAX_AMOUNT_3, 'fm99999999999990.0099') AS \\"TAX_AMOUNT_3\\", " +" TO_CHAR(AMOUNT_INCLUDE_TAX, 'fm99999999999990.0099') AS \\"AMOUNT_INCLUDE_TAX\\", " +" FNCGETFORMATTEDDATETIME(RATE_JUDGE_DATE) AS \\"RATE_JUDGE_DATE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(EXCH_RATE, 'fm99999999999990.009999') AS \\"EXCH_RATE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(HOME_CUR_AMOUNT, 'fm99999999999990.0099') AS \\"HOME_CUR_AMOUNT\\", " +" HOME_CUR_UNIT, " +" FNCGETFORMATTEDDATETIME(PUCH_ODR_INST_DATE) AS \\"PUCH_ODR_INST_DATE\\", " +" PUCH_ODR_INST_SLIP_ISS_FLG, " +" FNCGETFORMATTEDDATETIME(PUCH_ODR_SLIP_ISS_DATE) AS \\"PUCH_ODR_SLIP_ISS_DATE\\", " +" PUCH_ODR_STS_TYP, " +" INSPC_CMPLT_FLG, " +" FNCGETFORMATTEDDATETIME(INSPC_CMPLT_DATE) AS \\"INSPC_CMPLT_DATE\\", " +" FNCGETFORMATTEDDATETIME(CONFIRM_DLV_DATE) AS \\"CONFIRM_DLV_DATE\\", " +" SPL_ITEM_TYP, " +" ACPT_INSPC_TYP, " +" INV_CTRL_FLG, " +" WORK_ODR_CD, " +" OD_NO, " +" JOB_ODR_CD, " +" PUCH_ODR_COMMENT, " +" ODR_CD, " +" DETAIL_NO, " +" NON_NO_ITEM_FLG, " +" DRAW_CD, " +" SPEC, " +" MRP_ODR_TYP, " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(ACPT_QTY, 0), 'fm99999999999990.0999') AS \\"ACPT_QTY\\", " +" FNCGETFORMATTEDDATETIME(ACPT_CMPLT_DATE) AS \\"ACPT_CMPLT_DATE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(INSPECTED_QTY, 0), 'fm99999999999990.0999') AS \\"INSPECTED_QTY\\", " +" TO_CHAR(NVL(ACCEPTED_QTY, 0), 'fm99999999999990.0999') AS \\"ACCEPTED_QTY\\", " +" FNCGETFORMATTEDDATETIME(PUCH_ODR_EDI_ISS_DATE) AS \\"PUCH_ODR_EDI_ISS_DATE\\", " +" FNCGETFORMATTEDDATETIME(ODR_CANCEL_SLIP_ISS_DATE) AS \\"ODR_CANCEL_SLIP_ISS_DATE\\", " +" CONFIRM_DLV_DATE_COMMENT, " +" ODR_CANCEL_SLIP_ISS_FLG, " +" FNCGETFORMATTEDDATETIME(ODR_CANCEL_EDI_ISS_DATE) AS \\"ODR_CANCEL_EDI_ISS_DATE\\", " +" V_WORK_RLSD_PUCH_ODR_LST_2.ODR_CANCEL_CAUSE_CD, " +" V_WORK_RLSD_PUCH_ODR_LST_2.\\"STATUS\\" AS \\"STATUS\\" " +"FROM " +" V_WORK_RLSD_PUCH_ODR_LST_2 " +"WHERE " +" PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND PUCH_ODR_START_DATE <= TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI') " +" AND PUCH_ODR_DLV_DATE <= TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI') " +" AND VEND_CD = ? " +" AND ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND PUCH_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND(STATUS = ? " +" OR STATUS = ? " +" OR STATUS = ? " +" OR STATUS = ? " +" OR STATUS = ? " +" OR STATUS = ? " +" OR STATUS = ? " +" OR STATUS = ?) " +" AND WH_CD = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND V_WORK_RLSD_PUCH_ODR_LST_2.\\"PUCH_ODR_PERSON\\" = ? " +"ORDER BY " +" PUCH_ODR_START_DATE, " +" PUCH_ODR_DLV_DATE, " +" VEND_CD, " +" ITEM_CD"

"select " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_ANAME\\" as \\"VEND_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"where " +" M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD = SYS_MY_COMPANY.COMPANY_CD " +" and SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"CTRL_CD\\" = 'SYSTEM' " +" and M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" AS \\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR " +"WHERE " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" = ?"
"SELECT " +" M_WH.\\"WH_NAME\\" AS \\"WH_NAME\\", " +" M_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" M_WH " +"WHERE " +" M_WH.\\"WH_CD\\" = ?"
"SELECT " +" T_OD.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" AS \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_OD.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" T_OD " +"WHERE " +" T_OD.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" count(1) " +"FROM " +" V_WORK_RLSD_PUCH_ODR_LST_2 " +"WHERE " +" PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND PUCH_ODR_START_DATE <= TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI') " +" AND PUCH_ODR_DLV_DATE <= TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI') " +" AND VEND_CD = ? " +" AND ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND PUCH_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND(STATUS = ? " +" OR STATUS = ? " +" OR STATUS = ? " +" OR STATUS = ? " +" OR STATUS = ? " +" OR STATUS = ? " +" OR STATUS = ? " +" OR STATUS = ?) " +" AND WH_CD = ? " +" AND JOB_ODR_CD = ? " +" AND V_WORK_RLSD_PUCH_ODR_LST_2.\\"PUCH_ODR_PERSON\\" = ? " +" AND ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1"
